Class Instance

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.abstratt.kirra.Tuple
      • com.abstratt.kirra.Instance
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InstanceProtocol, Serializable
    public class Instance
extends Tuple
implements InstanceProtocol
    Represents an object and its relationships.

    Supports the idea of full vs. light instances (see InstanceManagement.DataProfile).
